de.rwth.i2.attestor.programState.indexedState.index

Class DefaultIndexMaterialization

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.programState.indexedState.index.DefaultIndexMaterialization
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexMaterializationStrategy

    public class DefaultIndexMaterialization
extends Object
implements IndexMaterializationStrategy
    A IndexMaterializationStrategy that uses a fixed right-regular string grammar given by the following rules:
    • X → sX
    • X → Z
    • Y → sY
    • Y → C
    Author:
    Hannah, Christoph
